reviewText:
Pros:
+ Colorful;
+ Pleasant interface;
+ Legitimate difficulty curve;
+ Some okay physics;
+ Challenging.

Cons:
- Pointless points;
- Graphics are below-average at best;
- Repetitive;
- Everything feels stiff;
- Pretty generic soundtrack...and by soundtrack I mean the crappy song in the menu;
- Can get boring.

On the border of Recommended and Not. Gonna go with Recommended because it kept me playing for a while.
